#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/solder_2d.rst:2
msgid "焊料检测 2D（Solder 2D，基于颜色比例）"
msgstr "Solder Inspection 2D (Color-ratio Based)"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/solder_2d.rst:4
msgid "**此页面的用途**"
msgstr "**What this page covers**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/solder_2d.rst:6
msgid "在焊料 ROI 内用 HSV 颜色范围对像素二值化，计算有效比例并与设定范围比较以判定 OK/NG，适用于 SMD 焊点的焊料检测。"
msgstr ""
"Binarizes pixels inside the solder ROI using an HSV color range, computes "
"the valid ratio, and compares it against the configured band to decide "
"OK/NG. Used for solder inspection on SMD joints."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/solder_2d.rst:8
msgid "**如何进入**"
msgstr "**How to open it**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/solder_2d.rst:10
msgid "模板编辑器中绘制对应 ROI 后，在参数面板中配置该工具的参数。"
msgstr ""
"Draw the corresponding ROI in the Template Editor, then configure the tool's"
" parameters in the parameter panel."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/solder_2d.rst:12
msgid "**操作流程**"
msgstr "**Workflow**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/solder_2d.rst:14
msgid ""
"**核心思路**：在焊料 ROI 内用 **HSV 颜色范围** 对像素二值化，计算 **有效比例** 并与设定范围比较以判定 OK/NG。一个 ROI"
" 可配置多组颜色范围（如蓝通道斜面焊料、红通道平面焊盘），分别独立设阈值。"
msgstr ""
"**Core idea**: inside the solder ROI, binarize pixels using an **HSV color "
"range**, compute the **valid ratio**, and compare it with the configured "
"range to decide OK/NG. A single ROI can carry multiple color ranges (for "
"example, the blue channel for the sloped solder fillet plus the red channel "
"for the flat pad), each with its own thresholds."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/solder_2d.rst
msgid "焊料2D ROI"
msgstr "Solder 2D ROI"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/solder_2d.rst:20
msgid "**参数说明**"
msgstr "**Parameters**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/solder_2d.rst:22
msgid ""
"**颜色公式（Color Formula）**：选择 HSV 或三色（Tricolor）公式；选择三色时配置 **三色 X / Y / Z / A** "
"系数。"
msgstr ""
"**Color Formula**: choose between **HSV** and **Tricolor**; when "
"**Tricolor** is chosen, configure the **Tricolor X / Y / Z / A** "
"coefficients."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/solder_2d.rst:23
msgid "**中心色调（Center Hue）/ 中心饱和度（Center Saturation）**：HSV 模式下色相基准点（位于色盘内部）。"
msgstr ""
"**Center Hue / Center Saturation**: the reference point inside the HSV color"
" wheel (HSV mode only)."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/solder_2d.rst:24
msgid "**起始色调（Start Hue）/ 终止色调（End Hue）**：色盘圆环边缘的两点，与中心点共同构成扇形有效色相范围。"
msgstr ""
"**Start Hue / End Hue**: two points on the color-wheel ring that, together "
"with the center point, form the wedge-shaped valid hue range."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/solder_2d.rst:25
msgid "**起始明度（Start Value）/ 终止明度（End Value）**：限定有效像素的明度区间。"
msgstr "**Start Value / End Value**: brightness band for valid pixels."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/solder_2d.rst:26
msgid "**有效比例范围（Valid Ratio Ranges）**：每组颜色范围对应的有效比例上下限；落入范围内判 OK。"
msgstr ""
"**Valid Ratio Ranges**: the lower and upper valid-ratio limits per color "
"range; an inspection is OK when the ratio lands inside the band."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/solder_2d.rst:27
msgid "**有效比例列表（Valid Ratio List）**：评估样本得到的各 ROI 有效比例统计，辅助设定合理范围。"
msgstr ""
"**Valid Ratio List**: per-ROI valid-ratio statistics gathered from evaluated"
" samples — useful when picking a sensible range."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/solder_2d.rst:28
msgid "**启用可视化（Enable Visualization）**：显示二值化 Mask 与比例统计（仅建议调试时开启）。"
msgstr ""
"**Enable Visualization**: displays the binarization mask and ratio "
"statistics. Recommended only while tuning."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/solder_2d.rst:29
msgid ""
"**使用共享参数（Use Shared Parameters）**：开启后，对同一组件下所有同类型特征共用一套参数；关闭后可对单个特征单独调参。"
msgstr ""
"**Use Shared Parameters**: when on, every feature of this type within the "
"same component shares one parameter set; turn it off to tune a single "
"feature independently."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/solder_2d.rst
msgid "HSV颜色范围挑选"
msgstr "Picking an HSV color range"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/solder_2d.rst
msgid "多颜色范围示例（蓝/红）"
msgstr "Multi-range example (blue + red)"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/solder_2d.rst
msgid "颜色范围二值化与比例统计"
msgstr "Color-range binarization and ratio statistics"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/solder_2d.rst:41
msgid "**三角形抽色（HSV 三角法）**"
msgstr "**Triangular color picking (HSV triangle)**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/solder_2d.rst:43
msgid ""
"颜色范围支持 **三角形抽色** 配置：在 HSV "
"颜色空间中，用一个三角形圈出目标颜色簇。三角形由三个顶点定义，分别对应中心色、起始色与结束色，比传统的\"矩形\" HSV "
"范围更紧凑、误抽其他颜色更少。可在 HSV 颜色块上直接拖动三个顶点调整范围。"
msgstr ""
"Color ranges support a **triangular picker** in HSV space — a triangle "
"bounds the target color cluster. The three vertices correspond to the center"
" color, the start color, and the end color. Compared with the classic "
"*rectangular* HSV range, the triangle is tighter and picks up fewer "
"unintended colors. Drag any of the three vertices directly on the HSV swatch"
" to adjust the range."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/solder_2d.rst:45
msgid "**多范围间的逻辑关系**"
msgstr "**How multiple ranges combine**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/solder_2d.rst:47
msgid "可同时配置多个颜色范围（例如：蓝色焊点 + 红色助焊剂）。系统对每个范围分别做二值化统计，最终判定时 **取所有范围的并集**："
msgstr ""
"Multiple color ranges can be configured at once (for example, blue solder + "
"red flux). Each range is binarized and counted independently, and the final "
"decision uses the **union** of all ranges:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/solder_2d.rst:49
msgid "任一颜色范围匹配的像素都会被纳入\"焊锡有效像素\"统计。"
msgstr "A pixel matching any range counts as a *valid solder pixel*."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/solder_2d.rst:50
msgid "颜色范围之间是 **OR** 关系，不会因为某一范围阈值过严而漏判其他颜色覆盖区域。"
msgstr ""
"The ranges are combined with **OR** logic, so an over-tight threshold on one"
" range doesn't cause the other color-covered area to be missed."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/solder_2d.rst:51
msgid "各范围的统计比例可在右侧参数面板中独立查看。"
msgstr ""
"The per-range ratios are visible independently in the right parameter panel."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/solder_2d.rst:53
msgid "如果不需要某个范围，可将其 *阈值* 调至 0，或在颜色范围列表中删除该范围。"
msgstr ""
"To disable a range, set its *threshold* to 0 or delete it from the color-"
"range list."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/solder_2d.rst:55
msgid "**抽色二值化预览**"
msgstr "**Color-pick binarization preview**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/solder_2d.rst:57
msgid "参数面板顶部提供 **抽色二值化预览** 切换，开启后可在画布上实时叠加显示当前颜色范围抽到的像素分布，便于调参时直观确认抽色效果。"
msgstr ""
"The toggle at the top of the parameter panel — **color-pick binarization "
"preview** — overlays the binarized pixel distribution of the current color "
"range on the canvas in real time, giving immediate visual feedback while you"
" tune."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/solder_2d.rst:60
msgid "**常见问题与提示**"
msgstr "**Common questions and tips**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/solder_2d.rst:64
msgid ""
"**焊锡阈值参数被 AI 更新拉飞**：避免把分数远超阈值的焊锡反馈为\"无错误\"——这会让 AI 学到错误的阈值。可在 **系统设置 → "
"模型更新器** 关闭 **AI 更新覆盖**，关闭后 AI 更新最多调整到设定的比例上下限，不会大幅突破。"
msgstr ""
"**Solder threshold drifts after AI updates**: avoid annotating samples with "
"a score well past the threshold as *no defect* — the AI will learn the wrong"
" threshold. Under **System Settings → Model Updater**, turn off **AI update "
"overrides**; once off, AI updates can only shift values toward the "
"configured ratio limits and won't break past them."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/solder_2d.rst:65
msgid ""
"**参数更新计算不准确**：检查训练集中是否有打分极端的反馈图片，移除明显错误或极端的反馈后重新训练。也可关闭 **更新颜色范围 / "
"更新颜色比例**，关闭后编程页面\"参数更新\"按钮将不会改动对应参数。"
msgstr ""
"**Parameter updates seem wrong**: inspect the training set for feedback "
"images with extreme scores; remove obviously incorrect or outlier "
"annotations and retrain. Alternatively, turn off **Update Color Range / "
"Update Color Ratio** — the *Update Parameters* button on the programming "
"page will then leave those parameters untouched."

